ition, the company operates shopping malls; develops residential projects; operates and manages Mohun Bagan Super Giant; and owns and operates the Lucknow Super Giants and the Durban Super Giants franchise. It primarily serves customers engaged electric power generation and distribution. The company was formerly known as CESC Ventures Limited and changed its name to RPSG Ventures Limited in January 2021. RPSG Ventures Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Kolkata, India."}}